Class DeviceSubscriptionDetail

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.smartthings.sdk.client.models.DeviceSubscriptionDetail

  • public class DeviceSubscriptionDetail
extends java.lang.Object
    Details of a subscription of source type DEVICE. The combination of subscribed values must be unique per installed app.
